# Eagle Peak Spur Salary Advance/IOU Request Form

This project includes a login page and a salary advance/IOU request form for Eagle Peak Spur employees. The form submission data is sent to a server for processing.

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Technologies](#technologies)
- [Setup](#setup)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Project Structure](#project-structure)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)

## Features

- User authentication with dummy credentials
- Conditional form display based on authentication
- Salary advance/IOU request form submission

## Technologies

- HTML
- CSS (Tailwind CSS)
- JavaScript
- PHP (for form processing)

## Setup

1. Clone the repository:
    ```sh
    git clone https://github.com/gachure1/advance.git

2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```sh
    cd advance
    ```

3. Open `index.html` in your web browser to view the application.

## Usage

1. Enter the username and password to log in (dummy credentials: `user1`/`pass1`).
2. Fill out the salary advance/IOU request form.
3. Submit the form to send the data to the server.

